casebody.data:
Jonathan P. ROBICHEAUX, et al., petitioners,
v.
Devin GEORGE, in His Official Capacity as Louisiana State Registrar and Center Director at Louisiana Department of Health and Hospitals, et al. No. 14-596. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 12, 2015.

Opinion

Petition for writ of certiorari before judgment to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied.
